{{Infobox dungeon |name = Tunnel to the Top |image = [[File:Tunnel to the Top.png|thumb]] |caption = A map of Tunnel to the Top. |tokens = 2,000,000 |location = Northeast of Snowslide Slope, east of Iceberg Ruins }} '''Tunnel to the Top''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Galar]]. It initially has 125 tiles arranged in two floors: 10x10 and 6x6 in size, respectively; including 16 chest tiles, 38 non-boss encounter tiles, 1 ladder tile, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 33,565,196 HP.
